sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as 客户端
    participant H as HTTP Handler
    participant R as Redis Lua
    participant P as MQ Producer
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant W as Worker
    participant D as PostgreSQL

    C->>H: POST /seckill<br/>Idempotency-Key=request_id
    H->>H: 获取 Semaphore<br/>建立请求 Deadline
    H->>R: Reserve(request_id, reservation_id)
    R-->>H: RESERVED
    H->>P: Send(message_id)
    P->>M: ORDER_CREATE_REQUESTED
    M-->>P: SendReceipt
    P-->>H: 发送确认
    H-->>C: 202 QUEUED

    M-->>W: Receive Message
    W->>D: BEGIN
    W->>D: INSERT consumer_inbox
    W->>D: 条件扣减 PostgreSQL 库存
    W->>D: INSERT orders
    W->>D: 标记 Inbox COMPLETED
    W->>D: COMMIT
    D-->>W: COMMIT OK

    alt ACK 成功
        W->>M: ACK
        M-->>W: OK
    else ACK 超时或进程宕机
        M-->>W: 稍后重复投递
        W->>D: INSERT Inbox ON CONFLICT
        D-->>W: 已处理
        W->>M: ACK
    end
